Invocation Name: motivation soundtrack
des:
Each of us has moments in life when things don't go the way we want it to be. This Alexa skill is created with the intention to help you get through those tough times. 

• Play a random motivational soundtrack 
• Cycle through soundtrack playlist by saying Next or Previous
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
